channel.title: Help with another Webclient error? Config 86?
channel.description:
Hello. I get this error when I run my client, which I am turning into a webclient, and jarring for more anti-leech. I tried deleting the cache and letting int redownload, But that isn't the problem. It loads through almost everything, up to maps. Then, after searching through some code, I found the thing it messes up on is the Unpacking Config part. I get a loaderror on config 86. Here is a picture. Thanks!
:mad: [IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/e1f.png[/img] :(
